# ldapwhois
# look up a user's display name in Active Directory via LDAP using Kerberos auth
# accepts username with or without @vetinst.no suffix
#
# example:  ldapwhois vi1234 
#           ldapwhois vi1234@vetinst.no
#           ldapwhois vi1234@ve
#           ldapwhois vi1234@vet
